# Dark-Room APP

## Author

[Noah Makau](https://github.com/nkmakau)

## Description

This project is used as an IP to practice on how to deploy a Node JS App with Jenkins Pipeline and send notifications to Slack and Email.

## Live Page 
https://young-waters-07809.herokuapp.com/


## Installation / Setup instruction
* Open Terminal

* Fork and clone repo from link provided

* Create cluster in MongoDB Atlas

* Create pipeline in Jenkins

* Deploy to Heroku using pipeline

* Merge test branch

* Add email notifications

* Add slack notifications remember to add emojis and any other message you need to add.

*Submit IP :)

